    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Dec 12, 2016</title>
      <link>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-12/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Dec 2016 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-12/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cloud security global market registering a CAGR of 23.5% from 2015 to 2020&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WhaTech The cloud computing market is prone to threats such as data breaches, data loss, and insecure application programming interfaces (API). Therefore &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.whatech.com/market-research/it/237165-cloud-security-global-market-registering-a-cagr-of-23-5-from-2015-to-2020-available-in-new-report&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.whatech.com/market-research/it/237165-cloud-security-global-market-registering-a-cagr-of-23-5-from-2015-to-2020-available-in-new-report&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Why combining technology with standards could combat fraud&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A recently published study illustrated the problem of fraud, with over two thousand data breaches confirmed during 2015, and around four billion cases &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.welivesecurity.com/2016/12/12/combining-technology-standards-combat-fraud/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.welivesecurity.com/2016/12/12/combining-technology-standards-combat-fraud/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;List of data breaches and cyber attacks in 2016  1.6 billion records&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;List of data breaches and cyber attacks in 2016  1.6 billion records leaked. Lewis Morgan 12th December 2016. I remember when I posted the final &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itgovernance.co.uk/blog/list-of-data-breaches-and-cyber-attacks-in-2016-1-6-billion-records-leaked/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itgovernance.co.uk/blog/list-of-data-breaches-and-cyber-attacks-in-2016-1-6-billion-records-leaked/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Is It Legal To Transfer Personal Data From The European Union To The United&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mondaq News Alerts (registration) &amp;hellip; effective 2018, which will have stricter requirements on U.S. companies with operations in the EU, including requirements related to data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.mondaq.com/unitedstates/x/552194/data+protection/Is+It+Legal+To+Transfer+Personal+Data+From+The+European+Union+To+The+United+States&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.mondaq.com/unitedstates/x/552194/data+protection/Is+It+Legal+To+Transfer+Personal+Data+From+The+European+Union+To+The+United+States&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;No password is ever complex enough for today&amp;rsquo;s hackers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Considering the number of data breaches we have seen this year alone and the millions of people that have been affected (7 per cent of the global &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/no-password-is-ever-complex-enough-for-todays-hackers/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/no-password-is-ever-complex-enough-for-todays-hackers/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Gemalto appoints Exclusive Networks as sole UK distributor&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; partners sell Gemalto&amp;rsquo;s products to exploit the growing focus on the EU&amp;rsquo;s upcoming General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.channelpro.co.uk/news/10260/gemalto-appoints-exclusive-networks-as-sole-uk-distributor&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.channelpro.co.uk/news/10260/gemalto-appoints-exclusive-networks-as-sole-uk-distributor&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Short Interest Reporting: Magal Security Systems Limited (NASDAQ:MAGS)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Post News The Firm offers integrated solutions for critical sites, managed by Fortis4G, its fourth generation Physical Security Information Management system &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.kentuckypostnews.com/2016/12/12/short-interest-reporting-magal-security-systems-limited-nasdaqmags-sellers-covered-16-04-of-their-shorts/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.kentuckypostnews.com/2016/12/12/short-interest-reporting-magal-security-systems-limited-nasdaqmags-sellers-covered-16-04-of-their-shorts/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Bill C-51 damages Canada&amp;rsquo;s economy. It must be scrapped&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; databases leaves Canadians and Canadian businesses even more open to being victimized by data breaches, cyber criminals and identity theft.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.thestar.com/opinion/commentary/2016/12/12/bill-c-51-damages-canadas-economy-it-must-be-scrapped.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.thestar.com/opinion/commentary/2016/12/12/bill-c-51-damages-canadas-economy-it-must-be-scrapped.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SANS and Carbon Black Announce the Speaker Line-Up for the Second Annual&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PR Newswire (press release) &amp;ldquo;The 2016 inaugural Threat Hunting &amp;amp; Incident Response Summit was an extraordinarily insightful and successful event for a sold-out crowd. This year &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sans-and-carbon-black-announce-the-speaker-line-up-for-the-second-annual-threat-hunting--incident-response-summit-300376519.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sans-and-carbon-black-announce-the-speaker-line-up-for-the-second-annual-threat-hunting--incident-response-summit-300376519.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;After a Data Breach, Don&amp;rsquo;t Throw Money at Customers. It Can Backfire&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Companies hit by data breaches may be tempted to generously compensate customers in hopes of repairing their public image and winning back &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dailyreportonline.com/id=1202774460936/After-a-Data-Breach-Dont-Throw-Money-at-Customers-It-Can-Backfire&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.dailyreportonline.com/id=1202774460936/After-a-Data-Breach-Dont-Throw-Money-at-Customers-It-Can-Backfire&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Oculus reveals Carmel developer preview, Google&amp;rsquo;s plans for HTML5, and&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to the company, the enterprise faces data breaches and cybersecurity threats almost every day. The new platform is designed to help &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://sdtimes.com/oculus-reveals-carmel-developer-preview-googles-plans-html5-segment-teams-bigquery-sd-times-news-digest-dec-12-2016/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://sdtimes.com/oculus-reveals-carmel-developer-preview-googles-plans-html5-segment-teams-bigquery-sd-times-news-digest-dec-12-2016/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What Hackers Want With Hello Kitty Accounts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This September, a hacker contacted Ars Technica and hacker-detection site Have I Been Pwned? with the stolen credentials of 2.2 million accounts &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.popularmechanics.com/technology/security/a24256/what-hackers-want-with-hello-kitty-accounts/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.popularmechanics.com/technology/security/a24256/what-hackers-want-with-hello-kitty-accounts/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Altitude and Panda Security Partner to Secure Information in the Contact&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Satellite PR News (press release) Both companies will work together to deliver endpoint protection, detection and response, data leak prevention and user/entity behavior analytics.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://satprnews.com/2016/12/12/altitude-and-panda-security-partner-to-secure-information-in-the-contact-center/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://satprnews.com/2016/12/12/altitude-and-panda-security-partner-to-secure-information-in-the-contact-center/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Survey Finds Many Enterprises Lack Tools, Skills to Protect Networks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to the report, only a quarter of companies have the ability to detect and effectively respond to data breaches. Furthermore, in a large number &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.eweek.com/security/slideshows/tripwire-survey-finds-it-pros-lack-tools-skills-to-defend-networks.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.eweek.com/security/slideshows/tripwire-survey-finds-it-pros-lack-tools-skills-to-defend-networks.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;TwoBirds goes Dutch for data protection hire&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; experience in advising clients in the media and telecoms sectors, focusing on issues related to enforcement, compliance and data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cdr-news.com/categories/people-and-firm/6923-twobirds-goes-dutch-for-data-protection-hire&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cdr-news.com/categories/people-and-firm/6923-twobirds-goes-dutch-for-data-protection-hire&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How To Enable Two-Factor Authentication on Yahoo Mail&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While data breaches may compromise your password and other information eventually, it is harder for them to affect a second factor of verification that &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2016/12/how-enable-two-factor-authentication-yahoo-mail&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2016/12/how-enable-two-factor-authentication-yahoo-mail&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
